Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.73,0:00:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.93,0:00:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.40,0:00:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.94,0:00:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.05,0:00:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.26,0:00:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.06,0:00:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.34,0:01:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.78,0:01:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.45,0:01:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.79,0:01:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.76,0:01:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团为了统治地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.90,0:01:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以无人操纵MD为主要军力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,创立新生OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.31,0:01:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.44,0:01:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于反对财团的功利主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.94,0:01:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的所有权力被夺去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.48,0:01:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,组织形态出现改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但藉着MD的高性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.28,0:01:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们快速地扩大了支配地域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.82,0:01:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.69,0:01:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于宇宙卫星认同了财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.56,0:01:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,财团下令杀死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.83,0:01:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全孤立的钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.90,0:02:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对他们来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.17,0:02:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,历史的洪流继续不断倒流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.07,0:02:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克…王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.98,0:02:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然鲁莽，但只有这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.79,0:02:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道很鲁莽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.62,0:02:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫我桃乐丝就行\N莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.53,0:02:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你也叫我莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.03,0:02:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.07,0:02:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下是时代的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为莉莉娜殿下你是我的偶像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.14,0:02:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十话\N[和莉莉娜的重缝]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一分队前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二分队待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.52,0:02:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,移动物体反应?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.22,0:02:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各队部署完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.30,0:03:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左翼有敌机!快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[红色一号]吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.42,0:03:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没理由啊，没理由啊，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是OZ的内乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,强行参战也只会成为目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标吗? 很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.79,0:03:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有命令要杀死\N和钢弹的有关的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.50,0:03:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要继续告诉罗姆斐拉我还生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.93,0:03:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是我的抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.81,0:03:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.94,0:03:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,显示特列斯派的志气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.28,0:04:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的…\N这样真的没问题吗?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.57,0:04:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充满野性呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.21,0:04:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸会，希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.01,0:04:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，卡特尔‧拿巴伯‧温拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎光临地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎光临战士的乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.49,0:04:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.13,0:04:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙刚才说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你误会了，我什么也没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.64,0:04:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想着OZ被消灭就好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.34,0:04:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想过和平的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派正迫近这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能动的男人\N就要参加支援部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.96,0:05:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我召集所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主义吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.86,0:05:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这地域为了得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.87,0:05:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拒绝参加军事活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里的特列斯派\N是在旧式政治下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被派驻保卫这国家的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.17,0:05:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们现在变成叛乱份子的反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.21,0:05:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是OZ内部的纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.05,0:05:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我们无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是自私的和平主义啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果驻军妨碍你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.35,0:05:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次就轮到完全和平主义倒下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.09,0:05:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军人保护自己的国民是任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则就会被当作障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.96,0:05:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一点也好\N我也想同情特列斯派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但无论如何，战斗会开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想在得到和平后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才慢慢开始讨论啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.17,0:06:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在战火中，没有和平主义吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.25,0:06:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，我只能袖手旁观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.02,0:06:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你，别介意，这是平常事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.46,0:06:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡乱反抗也只会令纠纷扩大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.26,0:06:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是旅客吗?   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.63,0:06:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你实在来到不好的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.27,0:06:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来的不是时候\N这里是个好地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.94,0:06:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了，今次很接近啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的艾亚利兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.49,0:06:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续引敌人过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别忘记进行干扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.44,0:07:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，全力出击消灭他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.28,0:07:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不向市民发出\N避难警告可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要小看我们的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派的叛乱份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会在城市前\N消灭他们给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确认战术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.17,0:07:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主力部队先攻，引开敌人先锋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.01,0:07:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,游击部队趁机攻击，侵入市内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭敌人司令部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.21,0:07:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事成后和主力部队会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.91,0:07:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驱逐敌人部队后，占据城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,游击队的指挥官是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红色一号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你，做得到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.46,0:08:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我是钢弹的驾驶员啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?有援军?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.54,0:08:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是能令兵力多寡逆转\N的精锐部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.11,0:08:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从前线调一部份\N过来消灭他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!敌人火力灭弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.56,0:08:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从中央突破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争太自私了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.84,0:08:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无辜的人最可怜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.49,0:09:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果参加这种战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.13,0:09:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就会迷失方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.81,0:09:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在增援来到前解决一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.81,0:09:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没发出避难警告吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红色一号!报告战况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻陷司令部了吗?红色一号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.83,0:09:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务更改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.13,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,镇压这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?你在说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，歼灭敌人机动部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接收到敌人无线电通讯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚…什么?   钢弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.92,0:10:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右前方的里欧\N好像是钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什么?红色一号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我!红色一号!红色一号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.68,0:10:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平民避难确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红色一号叫蓝色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.82,0:10:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是蓝色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.82,0:10:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?红色一号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.89,0:10:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何不回应我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作战失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多处中弹受损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暂时撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.39,0:10:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?红色一号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.93,0:10:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?有什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我!红色一号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红色一号!怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在完全和平的思想之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军备是不需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.79,0:11:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在把这思想传遍世界之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.29,0:11:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不是安全的国家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那种现状中，这么快就能和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,负起许多国家的未来的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.60,0:11:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起学习，我觉得很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一起想出尽快令战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.51,0:11:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从这个世上消失的方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.91,0:11:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝，你有意见?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.31,0:11:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果世上的人全是莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们就会马上认为战斗是蠢事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.32,0:11:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而战争就会从这个世上消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.16,0:11:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N如果大家是莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.83,0:11:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下的长处\N就不会显眼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.33,0:12:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得我的话\N听来有点虚有其表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但为何要进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家明知是愚蠢行为的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.71,0:12:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得马上就会有答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗为何不会消失啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝，什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人喜欢战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.85,0:12:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，藉着战斗来满足本能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.46,0:12:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果会有很多人失去性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对结果没兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使袖手旁观\N结果也会出现吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行动非常好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名为战斗的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是人拥的有最大魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.81,0:12:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类在历史里无数次不停战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.14,0:12:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像战斗是人类的生存目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.38,0:12:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我这样想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非不可以战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是一定要战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.39,0:12:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有另一个想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们应该能避免
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.83,0:13:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在未来重覆过去的历史悲剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争也须要那种聪明的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉着那种人的死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.84,0:13:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,历史会大大地变动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.97,0:13:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最终会成为这个时代\N的主要舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么回事呢…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝，你看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要我一日活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就会贯彻完全和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.92,0:13:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使我被杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.79,0:13:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这主义也会贯彻到底吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要害怕死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为死亡是在出生时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经被赐予的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.61,0:13:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，你放心，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了你的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常有用的骑士很快就会出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.85,0:14:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们一定能保护你的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.69,0:14:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人里好像有钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来会为这地域\N带来严重的损毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.17,0:14:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,市长如果坚持完全和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.80,0:14:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，这国家早晚会被灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别管，准备战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.28,0:14:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.24,0:14:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.28,0:14:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吗? 我很担心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.48,0:14:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里要开战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.22,0:14:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我准备暂时离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是新型的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一而再 再而三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.04,0:14:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些家伙真喜欢战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.51,0:14:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平比较适合我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这个国家有勇气决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.98,0:15:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们决定效法山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.68,0:15:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下，你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事?柏根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这个战乱的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倚靠山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.44,0:15:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赞成完全和平主义的国家\N变得很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.41,0:15:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有国家倚靠山克王国作为领袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.81,0:15:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的负责人有很大的压力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.98,0:15:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想即使是莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.58,0:15:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也会觉得疲倦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你，柏根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.45,0:15:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但这是我现在的生存意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.36,0:15:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果现在不努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.09,0:15:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为山克王国的君主就没意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.19,0:15:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，你的身心也太操劳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简直没时间让心灵休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.44,0:15:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柏根，不要说桃乐丝的坏话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.64,0:16:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她究竟在罗姆斐拉\N受过怎样的教育
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝是个聪明的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她或许比我更认真地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.48,0:16:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,思索这个战争的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.48,0:16:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想她终有一日会明白我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.72,0:16:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然诺茵小姐\N千叮万嘱要我保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.13,0:16:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我认为现在的莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.26,0:16:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有愈多朋友愈好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.87,0:16:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我要说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么回事?柏根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.77,0:16:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她查到钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.77,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛的下落?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.78,0:16:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐现正直接前去见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.41,0:16:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希…希洛回到地球了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.81,0:16:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他看来也很疲倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.08,0:16:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐想带他来山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.36,0:16:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛…会来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型机吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠里欧很难应付啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.12,0:17:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人在最后防卫网交战中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令部的撤退还未完吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.12,0:17:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惊惶失措的只是士兵们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他人很镇定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.33,0:18:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经厌倦战争啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厌倦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.20,0:18:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且有办法不战斗而达至和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.44,0:18:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们选择了理所当然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.41,0:18:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，许多国家和人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.21,0:18:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始追求完全和平主义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然没有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.05,0:18:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果在这个地球上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追求和平的人多过军人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.28,0:18:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个世界就一定会改变吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.92,0:18:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听闻山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.12,0:18:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被罗姆斐拉财团定为问题国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.66,0:18:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为许多国家开始和她结盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.83,0:18:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晚谁也不会再支持罗姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团急于进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.04,0:18:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因为他们害怕山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.91,0:18:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主义\N有可能在地球实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老伯，多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去山克王国
